latestIgtvVideos.title: Skincare Routine| My Go To Skincare Routine Is Back📍
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Let's get ready for the Holiday Weekend❤️
Hello Winter, its time to treat my Skin well. The Products used & suggested in the video are highly personalised. *But Useful for both Men&Women* ❤️ .
"Please bare with the background noice😂🙈"
.
All You Need: 
Coffee Powder, Coconut Oil & Moringa Oil(@kold_purepress ), Rice & Gram(Besan) Flour,Rose Water,Lemon & A STRAWBERRY🍓
.
.
Step1: 
1Tbsp Coffee Powder.
1Tbsp Coconut Oil 🥥 @kold_purepress
1 Tbsp Moringa Oil @kold_purepress
Mix Well and Apply.
After Scrubbing wash it off with Water& FaceWash(Cosmo)

Step 2:
1tsp Rice Flour
1tsp Gram Flour(Besan)
2tbsp Rose Water(Add as per Requirement)🌹
2 Drops of Lemon Juice(Optional)🍋
Wash it off with Water.

Step3: 
Its Time to use a Strawberry! 🍓
Strawberry is an Antioxidant,contains Vitamin C, Potassium, Fibre and Folic Acid and Extremely beneficial for heart health.
-Cut Half the Berry.
-Take a toothpick and make wholes in the berry -Rub it on the face.
-Massage and Rinse of Quickly (It has a little burning sensation) .
.
⭕Disclaimer: Test Patch First.⭕
